Interface INetworkMotorControllerEnhancedComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public INetworkMotorControllerEnhancedComponent
extends IFollowProvider, IFollowableProvider, IPercentOutputMotorControlProvider, IVoltageProvider

    Marker interface for a networked motor controller who has some smart features, but not others

    In the context of FRC, this describes a Victor SPX or other "slave" motor controller
